Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初  初次见面  我是仓部胜代
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:03.45,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仓部胜代  天才经理人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.18,0:04:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  之后就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部  部长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到罐头小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何  都只剩下最后48小时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.94,0:04:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,截稿日期已经不能再推迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.15,0:04:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一定没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:42.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我相信芥川老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊  文科系不是这样打气的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弄错了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这个笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:04:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦  没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢  虽然是低潮期
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不能一味消沉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芥川老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打起精神  噢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.22,0:05:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  我一直都只是帮运动部打气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文科系是第一次所以稍稍有点不安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.23,0:05:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芥川老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:18.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别叫我老师了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我丈途就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也请叫我胜代吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  小胜代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.87,0:05:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管事情来龙去脉如何  她是在帮我打气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是部长带来的  有点那个啥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.55,0:05:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么请坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.05,0:05:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原稿纸和笔都准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.09,0:05:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么需要的话尽管和我说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.96,0:05:55.90,Comment,NTP,0000,0110,0120,,{\fad(600,0)\an3\3c#000000\bord3.5}中午12点 : 2小时过后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.58,0:06:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我先去换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.29,0:06:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换  换衣服?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在  在那扇门的后面…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  还是想不出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.73,0:06:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平时的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.48,0:06:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这种程度就能写20页原稿的说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之要快点写出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专栏  连载  直接发表新作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:45.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  如果就这样一直写不出来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L O V E  芥川!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:07:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C U T E  丈途!  Yeah～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很高兴  但麻烦你安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.29,0:07:07.80,Comment,NTP,0000,0110,0120,,{\fad(600,0)\an3\3c#000000\bord3.5}下午1点 : 3小时过后
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人听说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.47,0:07:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于芥川丈途啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为截稿日期快到了所以请假了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像听说因为低潮而被监禁在罐头小屋了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他请假后清静多了也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便也给我变成正常人多好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,监禁?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.17,0:07:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  之前一直认为制服围裙这种着装很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来应该改变一下这观念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午饭很快就做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.35,0:07:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经好了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.45,0:08:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.95,0:08:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是第一次吃女生亲手做的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多吃点  补充体力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.25,0:08:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.17,0:08:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  趁热吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常补脑的胜代特制金枪鱼眼珠汤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  请吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  丈途同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途同学!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜代君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.28,0:08:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人身上在某种条件下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.19,0:08:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能变大6倍左右的器官是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.37,0:08:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男  男性生殖…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.78,0:08:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货  注意你的发言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.91,0:09:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是瞳孔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗的地方会变大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗的地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就来对下答案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来夏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然还有时间打瞌睡  你还真是从容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在赶稿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  睡了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你叫醒我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.20,0:09:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不抓紧的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.45,0:09:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是来拍写不出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工口小说的色情作家的照片而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  丈途同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.12,0:09:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仓部胜代啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.13,0:09:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.96,0:09:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  我去准备晚饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.38,0:09:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.80,0:09:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道她是谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天才经理人对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.14,0:09:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是被打气的人绝对会获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确  有她打气就可以说是获得了胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.27,0:10:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那个胜利无论何时都伴随着代价
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是胜代应援的棒球部的悲惨下场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.49,0:10:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的手机  怎么会在…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.21,0:10:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}等…等下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是丈途老师的经理人  叫仓部胜代
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找丈途老师吗  请稍候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是编辑先生打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在  说我不在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他让我说他不在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是这样的  请听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.85,0:10:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是电脑突然出了点问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不  我是用手写的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的家人去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍到好的照片了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.86,0:10:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就加油赶稿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.12,0:11:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了  我不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.83,0:11:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}丈途同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.41,0:11:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我根本没有写作的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,编辑其实也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.16,0:11:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这种事  丈途同学你一定能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请找回自信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这只手的错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.38,0:11:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我非写原稿不可
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}丈  丈途同学  不能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.68,0:11:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会有截稿日期啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  这种时间她还在努力着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.43,0:11:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也稍微  再努力下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.14,0:12:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手丈途同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途同学!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:25.33,Comment,NTP,0000,0110,0120,,{\fad(600,0)\an3\3c#000000\bord3.5}上午8点 : 22小时过后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着勉强自己读我的小说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:48.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  作为经理人必须
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.04,0:12:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解丈途同学所有的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  不会吧  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别  别过来…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到她居然叫了一晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要认输  加油  尽全力…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.60,0:13:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然做梦都在为我加油我很高兴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 我也困了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.27,0:13:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从来夏那里听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.51,0:13:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你和经理人都被关起来…了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  律  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.22,0:13:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天能不能也帮我请个假
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间实在是紧得不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧…紧?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真的是太紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忙着赶稿脱不开身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}难…难不成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:39.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱不开身?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.58,0:13:39.63,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雁字搦め:一种捆绑方法 引申为被事物缠身 不能自由行动之意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以…以你的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.76,0:13:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会有这种想法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.61,0:13:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我我我我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.01,0:13:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律 快背圆周率
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3.141592653589793238462633832795…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}不行了 我要睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:14:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜代君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位于加拿大萨斯喀彻温省北部的湖的名字是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.86,0:14:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,O Oman…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说清楚点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.29,0:14:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oman…Lake
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.27,0:14:13.24,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这湖的日语发音就和小穴(omanko)发音一样 胜代迫于无奈才改用E文
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再大声点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.15,0:14:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oman Lake
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再热情点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oman Lake
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.54,0:14:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像在恋人耳边低声诉说情话那样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.43,0:14:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oman Lake
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.91,0:14:24.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将要迎来高潮那样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oman Lake
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.89,0:14:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像喝着黎明的咖啡时那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:37.42,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去帮你跟老师请假 加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,律
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  律
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  继续继续…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  这是色情小说家芥川丈途的手机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.56,0:14:43.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}又来!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如有催稿以外的要事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请在听到哔～的声音后留言
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啵～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.72,0:14:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞定啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要随便接别人的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.20,0:15:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我想我是你的经理人  所以就得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  我这个笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.94,0:15:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再附赠个“笨蛋”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子没救了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.58,0:15:16.87,Comment,NTP,0000,0110,0120,,{\fad(600,0)\an3\3c#000000\bord3.5}中午12点 : 26小时过后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好饿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.24,0:15:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小胜代吗  门开着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谣江同学?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我听说在修罗场的作家很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.69,0:15:35.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就做便当带过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你添麻烦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.30,0:15:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有那种事  刚好我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要看  太丢人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为时间不太够  有些着急…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谣江同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.74,0:15:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  毕竟她是偶像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明很忙  却为了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.58,0:15:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现役顶级偶像亲手做的便当
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:02.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配上手上缠的创可贴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.05,0:16:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.29,0:16:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到得到别人的支持会这么让人高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.91,0:16:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太夸张了  丈途同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.78,0:16:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.58,0:16:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续写稿吧  我来喂你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.45,0:16:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点不好意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  味道如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.40,0:16:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我至今为止吃过的最好吃的便当了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  太夸张了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么老师  加油写稿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这双筷子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.78,0:16:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看都是谣江同学的私人物品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.07,0:16:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也  也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.29,0:17:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那双嘴唇接触了这双筷子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这双筷子又接触了我的嘴唇…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.26,0:17:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等于是  我的嘴唇和那双嘴唇…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是现实的破坏力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行得通  把这份激情投入作品中去…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.78,0:17:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  被运动部的人拜托去给他们加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.53,0:17:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.49,0:17:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好精致的便当
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的话  一起吃怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思  我肚子都饿扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  继续加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.51,0:17:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.47,0:17:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明差一点就可以想到什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:17:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:17:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是完全没有进展吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.97,0:18:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  还是完全没有思路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还不用着急  还有20个小时呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.53,0:18:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一小时…那个…该写多少页好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.69,0:18:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要引出情欲  首先需要遮掩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后则需要若隐若现展露出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是基本吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集中精神  用上我所有的感官
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我现在感受到的这份感情 现实的激情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要把它们变成文字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你偷看了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.22,0:18:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  一不留神目光扫到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了作品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我读了丈途同学的很多作品  所以我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了作品创作  这种事是必要的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.82,0:18:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.07,0:18:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.96,0:18:57.93,Comment,NTP,0000,0110,0120,,{\fad(600,0)\an3\3c#000000\bord3.5}晚上9点 : 35小时过后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩下12个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原稿写得怎么样了  完成了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.28,0:19:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了  接下来就是真正的修罗场了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.26,0:19:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在起  一分一秒目光也不能离开稿纸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么快写吧  我也要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.02,0:19:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fight oh! Fight oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go 丈途…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36}果然还是这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦汗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.20,0:19:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手  手…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请赐予丈途同学的手以奇迹…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个也不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  写出来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  我已经没法描写女孩了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.55,0:19:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会  就连这套珍藏的服装也不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了  我已经打算封笔了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.11,0:20:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不行的  丈途同学是天才色情小说家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.88,0:20:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不写色情小说怎么行…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以这么放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.33,0:20:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被这样绑着  我怎么能写得出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是我是经理人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了  给我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.89,0:20:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是说过火了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过无所谓了  已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.19,0:20:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈途同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回我总算是明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是女生所以才写不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我仔细想过了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.44,0:20:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天才肌肉同好会  高级健身家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.01,0:20:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健美肌肉～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:21:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么各位  为了丈途同学的色情小说家之路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.17,0:21:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽情为他展示男人的美妙之处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是肌肉男
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.29,0:21:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yoo 这是二头肌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.56,0:21:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yoo 这是腹肌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是胸肌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.04,0:21:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  丈途同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.77,0:21:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰到了  碰到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好硬  还很湿 而且好臭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请加油  芥川老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了   没法加油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.12,0:21:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是为了这个才来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记忆的走马灯!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.75,0:21:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健美肌肉～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.81,0:22:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在请假啊  丈途
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.36,0:22:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是被抓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.11,0:22:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是过度劳累住院了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.49,0:22:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是经历了很惨的修罗场呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.23,0:22:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住…院?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.24,0:22:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可怕  好可怕
